            <li>Build data governance framework</li>
            <li>Establish AI ethics and compliance policies</li>
            <li>Create AI center of excellence</li>
            <li>Invest in technology infrastructure</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Phase 3: Pilot Implementation</h3>
