          </ul>

          <h3>Phase 4: Scale and Expand</h3>
          <p>
            Scale successful pilots across the organization and expand to new use cases.
          </p>

          <h4>Key Activities:</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Deploy AI solutions enterprise-wide</li>
